import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
import "bootstrap"

import { createApp } from 'vue'

import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router'

import App from './App.vue'

import InicioPage from '@/pages/CrearPage.vue'
import VerPage from '@/pages/VerPage.vue'
import CrearPage from '@/pages/CrearPage.vue'
import HabitacionesPage from '@/pages/HabitacionesPage.vue'
import AcomodacionesPage from '@/pages/AcomodacionesPage.vue'

const router = createRouter({
    history: createWebHistory(),
    routes: [
        { patch: '/', name:'InicioPage', component: InicioPage},
        { patch: '/ver', name:'VerPage', component: VerPage},
        { patch: '/crear', name:'CrearPage', component: CrearPage},
        { patch: '/tipo', name:'HabitacionesPage', component: HabitacionesPage},
        { patch: '/acomd', name:'AcomodacionesPage', component: AcomodacionesPage}
    ]
})


createApp(App)
.use(router)
.mount('#app')
